  <original-body>Enhancement for `ActiveSupport::Base64` to implement url safe Base64 encoding (no `+` or `/` characters). Patch with tests attached.

- useful for easy random url-friendly UID generation (password reset links etc.)

@@@ ruby
ActiveSupport::Base64.encode64_url(ActiveSupport::SecureRandom.random_bytes) # =&gt; &quot;ykVB7nRN0kDH-MDgckZmpQ&quot;
@@@</original-body>
